| exportedClass item |
Display clear.
Transcript show: 'SOURCE'.
Transcript cr.
Workspace fileOutClassNamed: 'Exported'.
Transcript show: Workspace contents.
Transcript cr.
exportedClass := KernelInstaller classNamed: 'Exported'.
item := exportedClass new.
item setValue: 'ROUNDTRIP'.
Transcript show: item value.
Transcript cr.
exportedClass cr.
Transcript show: 'COLD'.
